{"data":[{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"0_1656717097.2046957","card_id":"Q_540836492","target":{"id":540836492,"title":"如何看待今日起，香港警员不再说「Yes, sir」，改成「知道，长官」？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/540836492","type":"question","created":1656597558,"answer_count":1558,"follower_count":2655,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[205,12968,28561,105508,2079626],"comment_count":205,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"“Yes Sir”这句英文，爱看港片的知友肯定不陌生。这是香港警员在回应长官时常用的敬语。从今年7月1日起，香港警队的步操口令、对答都将使用普通话、广东话。“Yes sir”改成“知道，长官”或“明白，长官”。从英语变成中文，小小的变化，却非常重要。在香港回归25周年之际，让我们向“Yes Sir”说声再见，喊一声“知道，长官！”"},"attached_info":"CkAIiaCfoPiUzrM3EAMaCDgyNDY3ODUwILbY9pUGMM0BON8UQAByCTU0MDgzNjQ5MngAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA","detail_text":"994 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/80/v2-c12604d039c239118b344c8a0332d633_1440w.png"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"1_1656717097.2055602","card_id":"Q_540762423","target":{"id":540762423,"title":"南京银行行长林静然「突发」辞职 ，南京银行开盘跌逾 9%，还有哪些信息值得关注？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/540762423","type":"question","created":1656570641,"answer_count":433,"follower_count":2569,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[1826,10575,19800,105508,129043],"comment_count":52,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"6月29日傍晚，南京银行突发公告称，公司董事、行长林静然，因工作需要、另有任用，于6月29日向公司董事会提交辞职报告，辞去公司董事、董事会风险管理委员会主任委员、发展战略委员会委员、行长、财务负责人以及公司授权代表职务，辞任自当日生效，行长职责暂由董事长胡升荣代为履行，在南京银行前任行长束行农涉案辞职并被查之后，接任行长刚满两年的林静然又突然辞去一切职务。受此消息影响，6月30日南京银行开盘一度大跌逾9%。"},"attached_info":"Cj8IiaCfoPiUzrM3EAMaCDgyNDUxNDQ5IJGG9ZUGMDQ4iRRAAXIJNTQwNzYyNDIzeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"797 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic3.zhimg.com